    <div class="titular2"><h3><span i18n:translate="genweb-heading_access_keys">Access keys</span></h3></div>

    <div i18n:translate="description_access_keys">
    Access keys are a navigation device enabling you to get around this web site using your keyboard.
    </div>

    <div i18n:translate="genweb-description_access_keys_more_info">
    In-depth information about access keys can be found at <span class="link-external" i18n:name="wcag">
